Economic Evaluation of Budesonide Orodispersible Tablets for the Treatment of 
Eosinophilic Esophagitis: A Cost-Utility Analysis.

Beauchemin C(1)(2), Castonguay A(3), Chan ES(4), Dellon ES(5)(6), Feagan 
BG(7)(8)(9), Ma C(9)(10)(11), Waserman S(12), Cook J(13), Claveau D(14).

