Health assessment of dams under various environmental conditions using 
structural health monitoring techniques: a state-of-art review.

Sivasuriyan A(1)(2), Vijayan DS(3), Munusami R(4), Devarajan P(5).

Author information:
(1)Aarupadai Veedu Institute of Technology, Vinayaka Missions Research 
Foundation, Paiyanoor, Chennai, Tamilnadu, 603104, India. sivarvind@gmail.com.
